<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <blockquote>
            <h2>Example of Template Engine</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Id ducimus iure reprehenderit incidunt eum sapiente quisquam, maiores commodi! Odio asperiores nulla vitae cupiditate tempora architecto perspiciatis, quis sed doloribus! Nesciunt.</p>
            <table width="50%" border="1" cellSpacing="0">
                <tr>
                    <th>S.No</th>
                    <th>BookName</th>
                    <th>AuthorName</th>
                    <th>Price</th>
                </tr>
                <% bookData.forEach((book,index)=>{ %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= index+1 %></td>
                            <td><%= book.bookName %></td>
                            <td><%= book.authorName %></td>
                            <td>&#8377; <%= book.price %></td>
                        </tr>
                <% }) %>
            </table>
    </blockquote>
</body>
</html>